   News & Events

    Best Practices

   There is an effort underway in conjunction with the CSR Advisory
   Committee to define best practices within study sections and to
   optimize consistency in operations across study sections. To this end,
   the following documents have now been completed and accepted by the CSR
   Advisory committee:

     * "Guidelines for Study Section Chairs"
     * "Role of the SRA.
     * "Submission and Assignment Process"
